title: Packers Back on Track; Power Rankings; Believe it or Not; Scott Pioli
itunes:title: Packers Back on Track; Power Rankings; Believe it or Not; Scott Pioli
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager and Victor Cruz break down the Green Bay Packers dominant win over the Detroit Lions! Then they dive into their 'Believe it or Not' segment where they answer the question: "Are we officially taking Tom Brady for granted?" They also talk with Scott Pioli; they share their fantasy waiver wire pick ups and are joined by Dan Hanzus for his power rankings!

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.
